    div.art 
      img(data-src='#{path}/2018_11_05.jpg')
      p.sub Oil on canvas, November. <br>More abandoned, than finished...based on Rembrandt's <a href='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Self-Portrait_with_Dishevelled_Hair#/media/File:Self-portrait_(1628-1629),_by_Rembrandt.jpg' target='_blank'>"Self Portrait with Disheveled Hair"</a>.<br>The meticulous few hours I put into this were certainly a labor of love...so this self-portrait is special to me, even though I tried very hard to not be precious about it!

    div.art 
