      p.sub Study of Caravaggio's <a href='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Lute_Player_(Caravaggio)#/media/File:1596_Caravaggio,_The_Lute_Player_New_York.jpg' target='_blank'>"The Lute Player"</a>. Oil on canvas, October 2018

